data.title: Festival Express
data.text:
(3) I'm not sure what this song is. The credits to the film list it as "traditional" - it sounds improvised to me.

The DVD has the following additional tracks featuring the Grateful Dead:

Hard To Handle Easy Wind

Other Dead songs that circulate as outtakes from the film include Candyman and Brokedown Palace.

Further Information

For more information on this recording see Matt Schofield's Grateful Dead Family Discography
